41da2ee3afcfb83850d631e37c9d6fb8105795a8ca92002c198a6eab08e457eb50861ed295a77535d302a956a4cc1fbeeec7ff0ba9b59a6e95a670506cbcb8e9  0001-src-x86-freq-freq.c-pthread_attr_setaffinity_np-is-n.patch
